CatDescriptText: Headline for related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 28, 1958, page A11, reads: "Alphas Host Brilliant 30th Anniversary Ball"
TitMainTitle: Man and woman wearing light colored dress with dark lace overlay, light colored belt, holding light colored textured jacket, standing on exterior steps of Hotel Webster Hall for the Alpha Phi Alpha 30th Anniversary ball
